title: Late 80's Houston Club-Vinyl-encoded in FLAC
description:
This is but a taste of the music which filled the dance floors of the clubs in and around Houston, Texas, such as Club 6400, in the late 80&#039;s.
All music is ripped from 12 inch vinyl records and are remasterd for maximum pumpage, so TURN IT UP!
